# Vendored libgit2 binaries ARE committed — the plugin ships with them to avoid
# requiring every contributor to build libgit2 from source. The Build.cs still
# gracefully degrades to WITH_LIBGIT2=0 when they happen to be missing, for CI or
# fresh checkouts on platforms we haven't built for yet.
#
# See Source/ThirdParty/libgit2/README.md for the build recipe used to produce the
# committed binaries.
